sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_snc_docdna_spoke.DocDNA</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>DocDNA</name><script><![CDATA[DocDNA = {
   username : gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.username"),
   password : gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.password"),
   logging : gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.log",false),
   endpoint : gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.endpoint"),
   production: gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.production",false) === 'true',
   rptID : gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.rpt_id"),
   fieldMap : {
      'case_number': gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.case_num_var") || 'case_number',
      'caller_id': gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.caller_id_var") || 'caller_id',
      'case_date': gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.case_start_date_var") || 'case_date',
      'claim_number': gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.claim_num_var") || 'claim_number',
      'doc_id': gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.doc_id_var") || 'doc_id',
      'folder': gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.folder_var") || 'folder',
      'content_date': gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.docdna.content_date_var") || 'content_date'
   },
   query:function(claimNum, caseNum, callerID, caseDate, docID, idxFormat, showBanner, annotation){
      //this.log("CASENUM\t:\t" + caseNum + "\nCLAIMNUM\t:\t" + claimNum + "\nMEMBERID\t:\t" + memberID);

      idxFormat = idxFormat || "XML2";
      showBanner = showBanner || "NO";
      annotation = annotation || "YES";

      var fieldQueryData = {};
      fieldQueryData[this.fieldMap.case_number] = (caseNum && caseNum != "") ? caseNum : false;
      fieldQueryData[this.fieldMap.claim_number] = (claimNum && claimNum != "") ? claimNum : false;
      fieldQueryData[this.fieldMap.caller_id] = (callerID && callerID != "") ? callerID : false;
      fieldQueryData[this.fieldMap.case_date] = (caseDate && caseDate != "") ? caseDate : false;
      fieldQueryData[this.fieldMap.doc_id] = (docID && docID != "") ? docID : false;
         
      var dynamicFields = this.getFieldQuery(fieldQueryData);

      var responseBody = this.sendSoapMessage("DocDNAExtractDynamicFields",{
         IDXFORMAT : idxFormat,
         SHOW_BANNER : showBanner,
         ANNOTATION : annotation,
         DYNAMIC_FIELDS : dynamicFields
      });
      if(responseBody){
         return this.parseResponseJSON(responseBody, "DocDNAExtractResponse");
      }
      return responseBody;
   },
   queryFullFile : function (docID, claimNum, caseNum, pageNumFrom, docFormat, idxFormat, showBanner, annotation, indexOnly){
      docFormat = docFormat || "PDF";
      idxFormat = idxFormat || "XML2";
      showBanner = showBanner || "NO";
      annotation = annotation || "YES";
      indexOnly = indexOnly || "NO";
      pageNumFrom = pageNumFrom || 1;

      var data = {
         PAGENUMFROM : pageNumFrom,
         DOCFORMAT : docFormat,
         IDXFORMAT : idxFormat,
         SHOW_BANNER : showBanner,
         ANNOTATION : annotation,
         INDEXONLY : indexOnly
      };
      data[this.fieldMap.doc_id] = docID || '';
      data[this.fieldMap.claim_number] = claimNum || '';
      data[this.fieldMap.case_number] = caseNum || '';
      
      var responseBody = this.sendSoapMessage("DocDNAExtractAnd", data);
      if(responseBody){
         return this.parseResponseJSON(responseBody, "DocDNAExtractResponse");
      }
      return responseBody;
   },
   querySpecificPages : function (docID, claimNum, caseNum, pageNumFrom, pageNumTo, docFormat, idxFormat, showBanner, annotation, indexOnly){
      docFormat = docFormat || "PDF";
      idxFormat = idxFormat || "XML2";
      showBanner = showBanner || "NO";
      annotation = annotation || "YES";
      indexOnly = indexOnly || "NO";
      pageNumFrom = pageNumFrom || 1;
      pageNumTo = pageNumTo || 2;

      
      var data = {
         PAGENUMFROM : pageNumFrom,
         PAGENUMTO : pageNumTo,
         DOCFORMAT : docFormat,
         IDXFORMAT : idxFormat,
         SHOW_BANNER : showBanner,
         ANNOTATION : annotation,
         INDEXONLY : indexOnly,
      };
      data[this.fieldMap.doc_id] = docID;
      data[this.fieldMap.claim_number] = claimNum;
      data[this.fieldMap.case_number] = caseNum;
      
      var responseBody = this.sendSoapMessage("DocDNAExtractPageSpecific", data);
      if(responseBody){
         return this.parseResponseJSON(responseBody, "DocDNAExtractResponse");
      }
      return responseBody;
   },
   queryAdvanced : function (searchValue, idxFormat){
      idxFormat = idxFormat || "XML2";
      var responseBody = this.sendSoapMessage("DocDNAAdvancedSearchIndexOnly",{
         IDXFORMAT : idxFormat,
         SEARCH_VALUE : searchValue
      });
      if(responseBody){
         return this.parseResponseJSON(responseBody, "DocDNAAdvancedSearchResponse");
      }
      return responseBody;
   },
   sendSoapMessage : function(soapFunction, paramObject){
      try {

         if (this.production) {
            this.username = gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.doc_dna.production_username");
            this.password = gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.doc_dna.production_password");
            this.endpoint = gs.getProperty("x_snc_docdna_spoke.doc_dna.production_endpoint");
         }

         var soapMessage = new sn_ws.SOAPMessageV2("global.DocDNA", "DocDNAWSMTOMSOAP."+soapFunction );
         if (!gs.nil(this.endpoint)){
            soapMessage.setEndpoint(this.endpoint);
         }
         soapMessage.setStringParameterNoEscape("QueryXML.RptID", this.rptID);
         soapMessage.setStringParameterNoEscape("Security.end_user", this.username);
         soapMessage.setStringParameterNoEscape("Security.user", this.username);
         soapMessage.setStringParameterNoEscape("Security.pass", this.password);
         var keys = Object.keys(paramObject);
         for(var i = 0; i != keys.length; i++){
            var key = keys[i];
            soapMessage.setStringParameterNoEscape(key, paramObject[key]);
         }
         var response = soapMessage.execute();
         var requestBody = soapMessage.getRequestBody().toString();
         var responseBody = response.getBody().replace(/>/g,">").replace(/</g,"<").replace(//g,"");
         var status = response.getStatusCode();
         this.log("STATUS\t:\t" + status + "\nREQUEST\t:\t" + requestBody + "\nRESPONSE\t:\t" + responseBody);
         return responseBody;
      }
      catch(ex){
         var message = ex.message;
         this.log(message);
         return false;
      }
   },
   parseResponse : function(xmlBody,nodeName){
      var resultNodeAddress = "/S:Envelope/S:Body/w:"+nodeName+"/Result";
      var xmlDoc = new XMLDocument2();
      xmlDoc.parseXML(xmlBody);
      //var resultNode = xmlDoc.getNode("/S:Envelope/S:Body/w:"+responseName+"/Result");
      var documentCount =xmlDoc.getNode(resultNodeAddress + "/ResponseXML/RESPONSE/DOCS_FOUND").getTextContent();
      var searchStatus = xmlDoc.getNode(resultNodeAddress + "/StatusXML/STATUS").getTextContent();
      var docDetails = {};
      var fileDetails = {};
      if(documentCount != "0" && searchStatus.toLowerCase() != "failure"){
         var documentNodeAddress = resultNodeAddress + "/Documents/IndexDetails/DOCUMENT";
         var fileNodeAddress = resultNodeAddress + "/Documents/FileAttachmentList";
         docDetails = {
            doc_id : xmlDoc.getNode(documentNodeAddress + "/" + this.fieldMap.doc_id ).getTextContent(),
            claim_number : xmlDoc.getNode(documentNodeAddress + "/" + this.fieldMap.claim_number ).getTextContent(),
            caller_id : xmlDoc.getNode(documentNodeAddress + "/" + this.fieldMap.caller_id ).getTextContent(),
            case_number : xmlDoc.getNode(documentNodeAddress + "/" + this.fieldMap.case_number ).getTextContent(),
            pages : xmlDoc.getNode(documentNodeAddress + "/PAGES").getTextContent()
         };
         fileDetails = {
            filename : xmlDoc.getNode(fileNodeAddress + "/FileName").getTextContent(),
            attachment : xmlDoc.getNode(fileNodeAddress + "/Attachment").getTextContent(),
            pages : xmlDoc.getNode(documentNodeAddress + "/PAGES").getTextContent()
         };
      }
      return {
         count : documentCount,
         status : searchStatus,
         doc_details : docDetails,
         file_details : fileDetails
      };
   },
   parseResponseJSON : function(xmlBody, nodeName){
      var jsonBody = gs.xmlToJSON(xmlBody);
      var result = jsonBody["S:Envelope"]["S:Body"]["w:" + nodeName].Result;
      var documents = result.Documents || result.DocumentList;
      var returnObject = {
         count : result.ResponseXML.RESPONSE.DOCS_FOUND,
         status : result.StatusXML.STATUS,
         documents : []
      };
      if(returnObject.status == "FAILURE"){
         return false;
      }
      if(documents){
         documents = documents.MASSEXTRACT ? documents.MASSEXTRACT.DOCUMENT : documents;
         if(Array.isArray(documents)){
            for(var i = 0; i != documents.length; i++){
               returnObject.documents.push(this.getDocument(documents[i]));
            }
         }else{
            returnObject.documents.push(this.getDocument(documents));
         }
      }
      return returnObject;
   },
   getDocument : function(document){
      var docDetailObj = document.IndexDetails ? document.IndexDetails.DOCUMENT : document;
      var pageCount = docDetailObj.PAGES;
      var retObj = {
         doc_details : this.getDocDetails(docDetailObj, pageCount)
      };
      if(document.FileAttachmentList){
         retObj.file_details = this.getFileDetails(document.FileAttachmentList, pageCount);
      }
      return retObj;
   },
   getDocDetails : function(indexDetailsObj, pageCount){
      return {
         caller_id : indexDetailsObj[this.fieldMap.caller_id].content,
         doc_id : indexDetailsObj[this.fieldMap.doc_id].content,
         claim_number : indexDetailsObj[this.fieldMap.claim_number].content,
         case_number : indexDetailsObj[this.fieldMap.case_number].content,
         content_date : indexDetailsObj[this.fieldMap.content_date].content,
         pages : pageCount,
         copy_number : indexDetailsObj[this.fieldMap.doc_id].LINE,
         folder : indexDetailsObj[this.fieldMap.folder].content
      };
   },
   getFileDetails : function(fileDetailsObj, pageCount){
      return {
         pages : pageCount || 1,
         filename : fileDetailsObj.FileName,
         attachment : fileDetailsObj.Attachment
      };
   },
   getFieldQuery : function(fieldObject){
      var queryString = "";
      var fields = Object.keys(fieldObject);
      for(var i = 0; i != fields.length; i++){
         var field = fields[i];
         var value = fieldObject[field];
         if(value){
            queryString += "<FIELD>";
            queryString += "<NAME>" + field + "</NAME>";
            queryString += "<VALUE>" + value + "</VALUE>";
            queryString += "</FIELD>";
         }
      }
      return queryString;
   },
   attachDocument : function (record, docID, claimNum, caseNum){
      var dnaSearchResults = this.queryFullFile(docID, claimNum || "", caseNum || "");
      if(dnaSearchResults){
         var document = dnaSearchResults.documents[0];
         var attachment = {
            file_name : docID + ".pdf",//document.file_details.filename,
            content_type : "application/pdf"
         };
         this.writeAttachmentBase64(record, attachment ,document.file_details.attachment);
      }
   },
   writeAttachmentBase64 : function (record, attachment, sa64){
      var gsa = new GlideSysAttachment();
      gsa.writeBase64(record,attachment.file_name.toString(),attachment.content_type.toString(),sa64);
   },
   log : function(messages){
      var gdt = new GlideDateTime();
      var message = "\n";
      if(typeof messages != "string"){
         for(var i = 0; i != messages.length; i++){
            message = message + messages[i] + "\n";
         }
      }else{
         message = message + messages;
      }
      if(this.logging){
         gs.info(gdt.getNumericValue() + message);
      }
   },
   type: 'DocDNA'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>jacob</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-19 18:52:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>193bd061db587f40604c9e7aca9619e0</sys_id><sys_mod_count>17</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DocDNA</sys_name><sys_package display_value="DocDNA Spoke" source="x_snc_docdna_spoke">e906146ddb187f40604c9e7aca9619cc</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="DocDNA Spoke">e906146ddb187f40604c9e7aca9619cc</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_193bd061db587f40604c9e7aca9619e0</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>jacob</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-21 10:07:19</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
